const aboutText = {
    init: "Welcome and thank you for visiting! My name is Michael Hazeltine and I am a web developer/programmer.",
    professional:
        "I have been working in web development since 2020."
        + "\nMy main project has been a career exploration"
        + "\napp (GoPursue) that I built entirely from the ground up."
        + "\nPrior to this, I worked as a teacher for the past 10+ years."
        + "\nI have experience with JS, React, Ruby/Rails, Python/Django, \nand HTML/CSS.",
    personal:
        "I live in DC with my girlfriend and two dachshunds."
        + "\nIn my free time, I like to work on and listen"
        + "\nto music, exercise, and explore the city.",
};

export default aboutText;
